" mujhe pasand hai  duriyon ka piyaar , mene dekha hai najdikiya akser fasle lati hai "

" Aap jese piyaar kerte hoo , use pure dil se piyaar kerna , cahe wo aapse piyaar kere ya na kere , aap apne dil ko sahi answer de paoge  ! "

" Ye tum kya sochte rehte hoo , in khayalon se bhar nikalke dekho bhar bhi ik duniya hai , Jaruri to nahi ye duniya hi sabki manjil hoo, muje pasand he mere khayalat , ye mujhe is duniya se bohot dur le jaate hai ! "

" Maine dekha hai , log aapki sari achi khubiyon ko bhul jate hai , jab aap koi galti kerte hoo ! "

"Try kerna apne aap ko khush rekho , ye duniya badi he matalabi hai , or aap bhi is ka part hoo ! "
